# Server Route Registration

The `GET /` endpoint listing is **auto-generated** via Fastify's `onRoute` hook. A module-level `registeredEndpoints` Set collects every route URL at registration time. Internal routes (`/`, `/docs/*`, wildcard catch-alls) are filtered out.

**No manual endpoint array maintenance required.** Adding a new route via `registerXxxRoutes(app)` inside a scoped plugin automatically includes it in `GET /`.

If a new route should be **excluded** from the listing, add its prefix to `INTERNAL_ROUTE_PREFIXES`.
